10. If any Man lyeth with Mankinde, as he lyeth with a Woman, both of them have committed Abomination;
                     Soddomy.
                   they both shall surely be put to Death, unless the one party were forced, or be under fourteen years of Age: And all other Sodomitical filthiness, shall be surely punished according to the nature of it.

11. If any Person Rise up by False Witness, wittingly and of purpose to take away any Mans life;
                     False-witnes
                   he shall be put to Death.

